<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV38">
<l>kaṭamā yiṉakaḷ kaḻittuttaṅ kālvaṉmai yāṟpalanāḷ</l>
<l>taṭamā yiṉapukku nīrnilai niṉṟa tavamitukol</l>
<l>kuṭamāṭi yimmaṇṇum viṇṇuṅ kuluṅka vulakaḷantu</l>
<l>naṭamā ṭiyaperu māṉuru vottaṉa nīlaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That they, rejecting [anything] that is forest, by the strength of their feet for many days</l>
<l>enter those that are tanks [and] take position in the water, is this penance,</l>
<l>o blue lotuses that equal in colour the great lord who danced after measuring the world,</l>
<l>for this earth and sky to shudder, dancing the pot [dance]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
